    "originContent": "Add to `~/.tmux.conf`:",
    "translatedContent": "`~/.tmux.conf`에 다음을 추가하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "ivgYKrHo9QnPgZYRA645sKpipVpw39MbuUN0CN9LfCA=",
    "originContent": "```sh",
    "translatedContent": "```sh"
